channel.title: Scar History Test
channel.description:
Me = Bored. So i made this to test your scar and other general rs cheating knowledge. Should be easy if you ve been around for a while. Maybe slightly harder for those who havnt.
It will ask you 10 questions. Picked down a list. You can retry and you will prob get a few diff questions.
Coudlnt be bothered amking forms with multi choice so i just used readln. Have fun and remember to post your scores.
*REMOVED*
Cause apparently aftermath doesnt care about this yet he decides to post. Xerxes is the leetest scripter on earth yet i have never seen any scripts from him and janibalo wants the question who made scar put in.
